function set_font(size) { mainbodyfont = new fontSize(document.getElementById('accessibility-text-size'), size); createCookie('ccsf_accessibility_fontSize', size, 365); updateFontSize(size) }

function getMainFont() { fontsize = readCookie('ccsf_accessibility_fontSize'); if (fontsize != undefined || fontsize != null) { fontsize = fontsize.replace(/px/, ""); //if font size is the smallest set button to inactive } else { fontsize = 12; } mainbodyfont = new fontSize(document.getElementById('accessibility-text-size'), fontsize); updateFontSize(fontsize) }

function updateFontSize(size) { //Reset all fontsize buttons to normal document.getElementById('fs1').className = 'inactive'; document.getElementById('fs2').className = 'inactive'; document.getElementById('fs3').className = 'inactive';

//If fontsize is 12 highlight small button if (size == 12) { document.getElementById('fs1').className = 'active'; } if (size == 14) { document.getElementById('fs2').className = 'active'; } if (size == 16) { document.getElementById('fs3').className = 'active'; } }

$(document).ready(function() { var start = document.getElementById("droptopnav"); var menus = []; for (var i = 0; i < start.childNodes.length; ++i) { if (start.childNodes[i].tagName == "LI") { menus[menus.length - 1] = new Menu(start.childNodes[i], "DIV", "dropshadowcontainer"); } } });

function submitSearchForm()	//validate search against empty string or default text { var query = document.search_form.q.value; query = query.replace(/^ \ s+| \ s+$/g, '') ; //alert(query); if ( (query == "") || (query == "Enter Keyword") ) { return false; } return true; }

document.getElementById('search-input').value = "Enter Keyword"; document.getElementById('search-input').hasBeenClicked = false; document.getElementById('search-input').originalColor = document.getElementById('search-input').style.color; document.getElementById('search-input').style.color = "#939393"; document.getElementById('search-input').onclick = function() { if (!document.getElementById('search-input').hasBeenClicked) { this.value = ""; document.getElementById('search-input').hasBeenClicked = true; document.getElementById('search-input').style.color = document.getElementById('search-input').originalColor; } };
